{"type": "article", "id": 21903, "title": "LVMH说不担心中国市场，以及，耐克设计师合作款抢先看｜浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了今天最重要和最好看的时尚新闻。", "date": "2016-02-04T10:40:45Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 466, "name": "LVMH"}, {"id": 23148, "name": "花王"}, {"id": 10443, "name": "Refinery29"}, {"id": 23149, "name": "时代公司"}, {"id": 12616, "name": "Dov Charney"}, {"id": 7776, "name": "NikeLab"}, {"id": 2855, "name": "Tommy Hilfiger"}, {"id": 19143, "name": "Public School"}, {"id": 12153, "name": "Riccardo Tisci"}, {"id": 671, "name": "Gucci"}, {"id": 23151, "name": "edwin"}, {"id": 1686, "name": "Marc Jacobs"}, {"id": 10224, "name": "Roger Vivier"}, {"id": 248, "name": "COS"}, {"id": 2540, "name": "Fitbit"}, {"id": 18988, "name": "TUMI"}, {"id": 955, "name": "VOGUE"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 75588, "comment_count": 9, "praise_count": 51, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607145622T2khwKyeEMfAgRlS.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<h2>一些重要的新闻：</h2>\n<p class=\"\"><b><a href=\"http://qz.com/608970/the-worlds-biggest-luxury-company-isnt-worried-about-china/\">LVMH 不担心中国市场</a> |</b> 首席执行官 Bernard Arnault 表示，分析师低估了中国的经济，经济起伏是有周期性的，而香港依然被看好。2015 年 LVMH 集团全年收入增长 16% 至 357 亿欧元，时装和皮具表现最好。</p>\n<p class=\"\"><b><a href=\"http://wwd.com/beauty-industry-news/financial/kao-corp-profit-cosmetics-10338403/\">花王实现双位增长 </a>| </b>截至 2015 年 12 月 31 日，花王全年净利润上涨 24.2% 至 988 亿日元，使用当前汇率，为 8.2 亿美元。营业收入同比增长 23.3% 至 1643 亿日元，即 13.6 亿美元。公司表示增长主要得益于成本削减措施，日元疲软以及国际游客的销售。</p>\n<p class=\"\"><b><a href=\"http://techcrunch.com/2016/02/01/refinery29-debuts-its-first-app-a-morning-news-round-up-called-refinery29-am/\">Refinery29 推出首款 APP</a> |</b> APP 叫做 \r\n\r\nRefinery29 This AM，这是一个类似于新闻摘要的晨间 APP，每天早上六点钟更新 8 张卡片的新闻，周末不更新。内容会包括世界新闻，流行趋势等，试图成为人们早上醒来后新闻获取的第一途径。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607145530pmTWow3IZGjl5JOF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.8490566\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\"><b><a href=\"http://digiday.com/publishers/powder-time-inc-brings-targeting-beauty-portfolio/\">时代公司进军美容电商</a> |</b> 时代公司 是时代华纳下的一个子公司 ，负责出版超过 130 种出版物，最为著名的是《时代》和《生活》。现在它正与一个美容网站 \r\n\r\nPowder  联合，这是一个个性定制化的电商，进入网站后首先需要填写诸如皮肤类别，需要解决什么样的问题，能够承受的价格范围等资料，然后网站会提供产品推荐。从战略上来说，这是一种大数据的采集。</p>\n<p class=\"\"><b><a href=\"http://wwd.com/retail-news/specialty-stores/american-apparel-rival-led-by-charney-in-works-10335952/\">Dov Charney 转而为新品牌工作</a> | </b>重夺 American Apparel 计划失败后，目前正与\r\n\r\nChad Hagan of Hagan Capitol（这个就是此前出资 3 亿美元企图收购的投资公司） 一起建立一个新的服装品牌，专注于美国制造的男女基本款服装，听起来和\r\n\r\nAmerican Apparel 没有本质上的区别。目前还没有更多详细信息。</p>\n<p class=\"\"><b><a href=\"http://www.nofashion.cn/a/1454485571528.html\">PVH 将全资拥有 Tommy Hilfiger 中国公司</a> | </b>PVH 将收购其剩余 55% 股权，将 Tommy Hilfiger 中国运营权全部揽入怀中。据双方声明，该交易扣除 1 亿美元现金后，价值约 1.72 亿美元，总估值约 4.95 亿美元，符合市场猜测。</p>\n<h2>一些值得一看的：</h2>\n<p class=\"\">Public School 在纽约发布 2016 秋冬系列，据说设计是以大卫·鲍伊为灵感。设计师周道一表示，此次系列让大家有种“navigate the new land”的感觉，层次与细节依旧是设计重点，同时体现出街头结合运动的美学概念。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071455308zk9o3aVmKfpWGTx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"3.02222222\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">Riccardo Tisci 和 NikeLab 再次联手，\r\n\r\n带来这双全新 NikeLab Dunk Lux High x RT 鞋款，以 Nike 最具代表性之一的 Dunk 作为蓝本，鞋身采用黑色皮革制作，在后跟拉标以 Riccardo Tisci 的 Logo 点缀，并搭载内植有 Lunarlon 气垫的大底。将于 2 月 11 日在北美 NikeLab 独家发售。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607145533NWdwPKl3exhUZC6I.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">GUCCI 日前推出了 2016 年春夏童装系列，\r\n\r\n从这一季开始， Alessandro Michele 所备受时装精英们喜爱的繁复华丽的“文青风”，也开始体现在童装上了。\r\n\r\nGUCCI 最早于 2011 年开辟童装线。为了跟随男、女装成衣线大刀阔斧的改革，品牌在去年 9 月任命了新的童装设计总监——Sandrine Delloye。她此前曾在 Marc Jacobs、Bonpoint、GAP 以及 BURBERRY 的童装部门工作。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607145534xRFI8vdzBNc7yfhg.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607145534VNC2JxFWU3I4KS9A.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607145535TQbKIwYf5P0MGmRp.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071455378UPLczF6VBEgsHtm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607145538LdlZHq8zxQScgR9D.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\">日本牛仔品牌 edwin 推出新男装线，叫做 END Edwin and Denim。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images multiple medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607145539GLXJkIVWyQx8pf0P.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.33466667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071455414z5jFbHcmhswrelB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.33466667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607145541TmaheJKnCQLv5q1r.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.33466667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607145542TISfWrlzbx4QLk53.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.33466667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607145543CjwhMWoKfDpy1zHg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.33333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071455430HyMPGR8i7sr4g9I.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.33333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071455443FIyeaHksGguREri.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.33333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607145547tShkTLiF81w7gerV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.33466667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607145547av407IyTwKCuxWjU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.33466667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\"><br></p>\n<p class=\"\">Marc Jacobs 推出情人节限定系列，设计很直白，只是将爱心放在手包、本子、手机壳等小物件上。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images multiple medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607145548G30QlwWqE6oDzMvZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607145548m90nghYHLeqJCkvR.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607145549Lk3vCAnbZqsmxj09.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images multiple medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607145550QiP4mxlN8hyO7Lru.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607145550RaB2EcZwog3nFsl0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607145551fwLjWsASkmZiCJYn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\">又是一款能够用来当情人节礼物的单品，Roger Vivier 把源于 70 年代的红唇图案再次放在了手拿包和芭蕾鞋上。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607145551iS8mpzBt1kvGRAal.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.41201717\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607145553mFuUGIXV3jvtiAy9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.24708171\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607145554yTVrM2fjemFnKhXW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.44444444\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607145555etUZ2Dy7QFlfdh3Y.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71830986\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\">COS 推出新款女装，选用了各种中性色调，包括象牙白、驼色与海军蓝，加上利落、简约的剪裁，设计出来的不规则剪裁连身裙、泡泡袖衬衫、A 字中长裙、牛仔tubedress 等，\r\n\r\n广告拍摄选址在了加州沙漠上，简约的设计和背景呼应。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images multiple medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607145556ihC9wQxcpWbgKaBU.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"1.50093809\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071455571Zyurfp65dK023IS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.50093809\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607145557uQwZOY0VaXxpETFC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.50093809\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607145558Nh6iMACHL2fl98XK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.50093809\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607145559jX09fpveNMaSdom1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.50093809\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607145600zZGsuV0RJgU19r4f.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.50093809\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071456010e72HvNWB3wnyQOx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.50093809\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607145602BpqtzbFhj8l61PiH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.50093809\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607145602M1u4g7pYktEfrxVJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.50093809\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\">Fitbit 发布更为时尚的运动手环，叫做 Fitbit Alta，一次充电使用时间长达 5 天，售价 130 美元左右，将在 3 月 1 日正式发售。今年晚一些，Tory Burch 与 Fitbit 的合作将再次推出。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607145603kBZM7IUXN6PaF2WT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607145604Bo4CzkD8JIpNA5FV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\"><br></p>\n<p class=\"\">国际知名旅行装备品牌 TUMI 近年大举进驻潮流界，先后与 Public School 和 SOPHNET. 甚至与巴黎时尚名所 colette 推出别注系列，而主线产品同样出生，最近更委任了纽约设计师 Michael Petry 接替 George Esquivel 成为品牌创意总监。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607145605zB6jmDxyhHAYXC5q.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66759259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607145605lTmAVRzwv6koqW2L.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66759259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607145606IGlshix8W4LgTyC5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66759259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607145611JnlcT6bzqLwEriYQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66759259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607145612SEBuaL1b9pzrGlCV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66759259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607145612mThSXp6nYEZzugCt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66759259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\">VOGUE 发布了一本 zine，看起来很 70 年代地下音乐风，只有 32 页，发行 100。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607145614VlReYU3vJbKLpTZQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607145615oAwiSJbEpqWYXsyv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607145616kj5EPQXne87JRwIm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607145617n8LZoPmXHjvQKryp.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607145618cB9lsECPvZmHIepK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607145619RG46m0BDa8rz5WUF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.24352332\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\"><br></p>\n\n\n"}